latestPosts.caption:
A sunscreen with spf 50 that’s suitable for acne prone skin has been FOUND✨

This multifunctional sun cream moisturizes and soothes skin while offering anti-aging effects. The organic sunscreen is fitted with SPF 50+ PA++++ for UV protection and formulated with 10,000ppm of F-CICA COMPLEX (containing seven centella asiatica derivatives fermented with yeast) for soothing effects. 

Enriched with brightening agents like niacinamide, the chemical sunscreen leaves a glowing finish. Vegan formula absorbs quickly into skin without leaving a white cast.
